data.description: Rare-2 Master Bedrooms! Each bedroom has a full bathroom attached! Sandpiper Lakes Condo 2 bedroom/2.5 bath. Features include an open concept design and a vaulted ceiling in the Great Room and a balcony overlooking the space below. The warm gas log fireplace in the living area and sliding doors lead out to a concrete patio. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets and counter space and all of the appliances are new and are included. Appliances include New Refrigerator, Dishwasher-Amana, Range/Oven-GE, Microwave, Micro-Hood, 50 Gallon Water Heater, and new carpet. The large window brightens the kitchen and there is also room for a dinette. Adjacent is a formal dining area that is really flexible space. There is a half bath just off the foyer and two closets for convenient storage. On the 2nd level, both bedrooms have private 4 piece bathrooms and large walk-in closets. One bath and closet has new tile flooring and one bedroom has access to a deck. The laundry is on the second level and both the Washer and Electric Dryer will stay with the condo. There is a one car attached garage, attic storage. The lake is just across the street where residents may fish or just enjoy the view! Nice and quiet located on a Cul-De-Sac in the back, yet the convenience of being close to shopping, dining, Ball State and IU Health. Maintenance fee $190 due monthly. Rare 2 Bedrooms each with En-suite for convenient living.
